# Advanced Core Features Redesign (Special Edition)

The goal is to transform the "Core Features" section into a high-fidelity, interactive experience that breaks the standard grid layout.

## Proposed Changes

### [Zeta Capital Website]

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/index.html)
- Replace the `grid-3` with an `advanced-feature-grid` (Staggered Bento-style).
- Add "Decorative Glows" (`<div class="glow-point"></div>`) inside feature cards.
- Add "Floating Icon Wrappers" to allow icons to break the card boundaries.
- Update feature descriptions to include "Value Subtitles".

#### [MODIFY] [style.css](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/css/style.css)
- Implement `.advanced-feature-grid` (CSS Grid with `grid-template-areas`).
- Add `.feature-card-special` with `overflow: visible`, `perspective: 1000px`, and `transform-style: preserve-3d`.
- Define `@keyframes glow-pulse` for background accents.
- Add magnetic hover effects logic in CSS.

#### [MODIFY] [js/main.js](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/zeta/js/main.js)
- Implement a simple "Magnetic Card Tilt" function that responds to mouse movement over the features section.

